  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Pre-Phase 1 prospective, non-interventional clinical assessment study to evaluate
      Crigler-Najjar syndrome subjects requiring daily phototherapy, aged 1 year and older.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
